  "description": "A single bird, likely a tern due to its pointed wings and beak, is captured in mid-flight against a bright blue sky. The bird is angled diagonally, its wings spread wide. The sky has a very slight gradient, with a lighter shade of blue at the top and a slightly deeper tone towards the bottom. There is subtle cloud cover creating a soft atmospheric effect. The bird's body is dark grey while the underside of its wings appear lighter. Its beak is long and pointed.",
